def transform(sequence):
    nums = list(map(int, sequence))
    sum_nums = sum(nums)
    transformed_sequence = ['0'] * nums.count(0) + ['1'] * nums.count(1) + ['3'] * nums.count(3) + ['8'] * nums.count(8) + [str(sum_nums)[-1]]
